title: 1 Bed / 1 Bath Westwood Apartment in Great Location w/ Balcony/Parking
posting_body: ['Viewing by appointment only.', 'This 1 bedroom offers the following features:', 'Central Air', 'Refrigerator', 'Carpet in Bedroom', 'Wood Flooring', 'Fireplace', 'Granite Countertops', 'Dishwasher', 'Private Balcony', 'Stove and Oven', '1 bedroom 1 bath apartment with wood flooring in the living room and carpeted bedroom.', 'Apartment has a gas fireplace, central air, a private balcony.', 'Kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, a stove, an oven, a dishwasher and a refrigerator.', 'Our gated access community proudly offers features such as a soothing spa, a fitness center, disability access, a picnic area with barbecue, and onsite maintenance.', 'Underground parking included and storage available.', 'Minutes away to all popular Westside destinations including Armand Hammer Museum of Art & Cultural Center, UCLA, Getty Museum, Geffen Playhouse, Wadsworth Theatre.', 'Fabulous restaurants and shopping, movie theatres, world class yoga, and public transportation are all at your fingertips.', 'For appointment or for questions, call us at', 'show contact info', '.', 'For more property photos, floor plans and further details visit: <URL>', '1441 Midvale Avenue', 'Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024', 'The building amenities include the following features:', 'Laundry Facilities', 'Sauna', 'Spa', 'Fitness Center', 'Controlled Access', 'BBQ/Grill Area', 'Assigned Parking', 'Elevator', 'Disclaimer: Pictures are a representation but may not be of the exact apartment.', 'Advertised unit availability, rental rates, and terms are updated every 24 hours and conditions are subject to change without notice.', 'Please call for latest availability details.']
